Merchant submits shipment form
        │
        ▼
POST /api/merchant/shipment
        │
        ▼
shipment.service.js
  → validate fare config
  → create Shipment in DB (status: PENDING)
  → create ShipmentLog in DB
  → publishEvent(ROUTING_KEY.SHIPMENT_CREATED, payload)  ← RabbitMQ enters HERE
        │
        ▼
RabbitMQ Exchange: porter.shipments
routing key: shipment.created
        │
        ▼
Queue: dispatcher.new_shipments
        │
        ▼
dispatcher.consumer.js (already running, listening)
  → fetch full shipment from DB
  → io.to("dispatchers").emit("shipment:new", shipment)  ← Socket.IO
        │
        ▼
All connected Dispatcher UIs see the new shipment on their board
        │
        ▼
Dispatcher clicks "Assign" → picks a rider
        │
        ▼
PATCH /api/dispatcher/shipment/:id/assign
        │
        ▼
dispatcher.service.js
  → update Shipment in DB (status: ASSIGNED, riderId)
  → create ShipmentLog
  → publishEvent(ROUTING_KEY.SHIPMENT_ASSIGNED, payload)  ← RabbitMQ again
        │
        ▼
Queue: notifications.rider + notifications.merchant
        │
        ▼
notification.consumer.js
  → io.to("user:riderId").emit("shipment:assigned", ...)
  → io.to("user:merchantId").emit("shipment:assigned", ...)